@MatchPlanActivation
Feature: MatchCalculation_CPCEEP

Scenario Outline:Payroll Match Calculation Feature -Single file upload
Given Model is selected for the endpoint "/api/Source/SaveSource"
When Configuration has been made as per following
| propertyName                       | value                  |
| sourceName                         | ERMatch                |
| sourceType                         | 2                      |
| sourceCategory                     | 6                      |
| sourceCode                         | D                      |
| effectiveStartDate                 | 01/01/2015             |
| responsibleMode                    | <ResponsibleMode>      |
| isThresholdApplicable              | <Threshold>            |
| isTrueUpApplicable                 | <TrueUp>               |
| isCatchApplicable                  | <CatchUp>              |
| isCalculationSuspended             | <CalcSuspended>        |
| eligiblePaymentType                | 1                      |
| employerContributionType           | <ContributionType>     |
| percentageOfCalculation            | <Percentage of Calc>   |
| percentageOfCompensation           | <Percentage of Comp>   |
| periodForCalculation               | 0                      |
| limitMaximumPercentage             | 50                     |
| limitMinimumPercentage             | 10                     |
| maximumPercentageCompensation      | 60                     |
| firstTierMatchPercent              | <First-TierMatch>      |
| firstTierCompensationMatchPercent  | <First-TierMatchComp>  |
| secondTierMatchPercent             | <Second-TierMatch>     |
| secondTierCompensationMatchPercent | <Second-TierMatchComp> |
| thirdTierMatchPercent              | <Third-TierMatch>      |
| thirdTierCompensationMatchPercent  | <Third-TierMatchComp>  |

And Collection in a model is configured with 2 blocks for the property "SourceOfMatch" with values as given below
| BlockNumber | Key      | Value            |
| 1           | SourceId | <PretaxSourceID> |
| 2           | SourceId | <RothSourceID>   |

And API request has been sent to the "IPlanDetailsSave" with the method name "SaveSource"

Given Payroll file "CombinedFile.csv" is selected and Edit payroll file as mentioned below
| Key                   | Value       |
| HIRE DATE             | <HireDate>  |
| MOST RECENT TERM DATE | <TermDate>  |
| HOURS                 | 1000        |
| PAY DATE              | <PayDate>   |
| BIRTH DATE            | <BirthDate> |
| PLAN COMPENSATION     | <PlanComp>  |
| GROSS COMPENSATION    | 1000        |
| Pretax                | <Pretax>    |
| Roth                  | <Roth>      |
| ERMatch               | <ERMatch>   |

When File upload is executed for the file "CombinedFile.csv"

Then API should respond Match Calculated values as
| SourceName  | CalculatedAmount   | PP Amount        | YTD Amount        |
| ERMatch     | <ERMatch_Calc>     | <ERMatch_PP>     | <ERMatch_YTD>     |

Then API should give response as "<Validation>"

